ভণ্ড</span><span class=\"english\">) </span><span class=\"english\">অথবা</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">ছক</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">অঙ্কন</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">করে</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">বামপাশে প্রদত্ত </span><span class=\"english\">বাগ্‌ধারার</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">সাথে ডানপাশে প্রদত্ত </span><span class=\"english\">অর্থের</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">সঠিকভাবে মিল করার জন্য </span><span class=\"english\">বরাদ্দকৃত</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">নম্বর</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">পাবে</span><span class=\"english\">।</span><span> </span></p><p><span class=\"english\">*</span><span class=\"english\">বি.দ্র</span><span class=\"english\">, </span><span class=\"english\">রোমান</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">নম্বর</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">যেহেতু</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">উল্লেখ</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">নেই</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">তাই</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">কেউ</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">রোমান</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">নম্বর</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">বা</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">অন্য</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">যেকোনো</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">প্রতীক</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">বা</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">চিহ্ন</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">ব্যবহার</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">করলে</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">প্রাপ্ত</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">নম্বর</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">থেকে</span><span class=\"english\"> ০১ </span><span class=\"english\">নম্বর</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">কর্তন</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">করতে</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">হবে</span><span class=\"english\">।</span></p><p><span class=\"english\">*</span><span class=\"english\">পরীক্ষক</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">ভুলগুলো</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">আন্ডারলাইন</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">করে</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">অবশ্যই</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">ঠিক</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">করে</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">দিবেন</span><span class=\"english\">।</span></p>"
