        "question_html": "<p><span class=\"english\">Write meaningful sentences of your own with each of the following words/phrases.</span><span><span> </span></span><span class=\"english\"><span> </span>5</span></p><p><span class=\"english\">Irregular, Perseverance, Plight, Immensely, Heart and soul </span></p>",
